Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,[Bakuman Episode 19 Translation by Kewl0210]
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{Eyecatch}
Comment: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:49.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.28,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:17.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, sometime during summer vacation I'll write an interesting name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:22.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi received a response from a company, asking her to write more of her cell phone novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:29.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it natural to want to be with someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:32.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you and Azuki aren't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:37.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:26.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:29.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I'm drawing manga on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:31.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! W-Why?! {KmE: "Eh" wasn't on the script but it looks weird when i join these 2 lines without it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have to ask why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to become a mangaka, you need to honor your deadlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:42.55,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:55.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really like the idea of you and Miyoshi being there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, in that respect, you've got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi's presence wasn't the reason why I couldn't write a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It was the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:11.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought that if I got serious with Miyoshi, it would definitely make me want to sell even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:16.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I also thought it might even be a good idea not to meet until our dreams come true, like with you and Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Love comes in many forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:24.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I wasn't doing this for a girl, but now I think I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:27.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.62,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I did have that part wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:35.08,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But in that case, you really can't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.61,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely gonna be the original story author of a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:41.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I need to pair up with someone besides you, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:50.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The artwork in your names really sucks, Shuujin, so tell me when you finish and I'll do a good copy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,If you give it to somebody else, they won't have a clue what's going on in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:55.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll charge you 100 yen a page.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:10.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Also, if I do something alone, is it okay for me to change the pen name from Ashirogi Muto to {\i1}Ashiro{\i0} Muto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:11.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:14.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,If you're writing alone, then just use "Mashiro Moritaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.77,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.74,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm fine with it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.28,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What're you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.46,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,The new term's opening ceremony is starting soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:33.73,Main,Miyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,I was up so late thinking that I overslept! {Someone check this, it's inaudible.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,See ya Saikou, let's both do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.46,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine, let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.81,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! That's not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.74,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault for not honoring my deadline, so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.28,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:05.30,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it? Because you were spending so much time with me over summer vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.57,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's not why!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We may have been together, but I was thinking of the scenario for the manga the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:14.08,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But then if you just explain it to Mashiro like that, I'm sure he'll understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.94,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go tell him that—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:15.96,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.13,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making excuses to Mashiro for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.31,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And not to Azuki either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:23.40,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault, so don't go butting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:25.77,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou knows it wasn't your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:30.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still gonna be an original manga story author!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And Saikou's still gonna be a mangaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:39.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, so I'm gonna keep working hard. I still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.97,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,When I said that, even Saikou understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.44,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Because you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:46.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.25,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep doing my best for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:55.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But if you say something unnecessary to Saikou or Azuki, I'm sure I won't like you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.75,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.92,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You want to do it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.98,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two have a fight or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We're not little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.72,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a name, just a plan for the setup. {Please don't change the word "setup" to something else.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.69,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,A con man and a detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.48,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,He sets traps for the culprits in order to bring out the truth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:31.17,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you do this kind of mystery story right, it really will be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:35.41,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, for this kind of story in particular, we really need Takagi-kun's power, don't we?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.36,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Have you given up on doing a mainstream battle manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.00,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a kind of mainstream story too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:41.87,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:45.67,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is mainstream, and a kind that Ashirogi Muto is more suited to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.92,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I drank a little too much coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.78,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:51.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.85,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-kun, it's Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.93,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you break up your team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.01,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun wouldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:07.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't keep my promise to write a name by the end of summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.03,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.29,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun sure is strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how serious he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:17.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't think I was suited to battle manga from the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:22.54,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,but Mashiro was fixated on doing a battle story, so we had that conflict of opinions too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.04,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So this time, I'm writing a mystery story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.92,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,A mystery story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:32.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And uh, you'll look at the name if it's just me right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.03,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll look at it. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:40.47,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,So... Mashiro-kun doesn't know you're drawing a mystery story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell him that I'm ignoring his wishes and writing something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:48.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on having it done by the end of summer vacation, but I couldn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.22,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm setting my sights on being an original story author by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.22,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with these two?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:58.45,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I tell Takagi-kun what story Mashiro-kun is trying to do, then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.45,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:02.34,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, a mystery story sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.80,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It really fits you, Takagi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.05,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Get that name in soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even though I'd like to get it done soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:09.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't have the setup plan for the protagonist done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.42,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The protagonist can just be an ordinary detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.48,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The important things in a mystery story are the tricks and mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.30,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.43,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You have talent, Takagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:21.43,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always telling you that even the editorial department has acknowledged that, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.55,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.94,Main,Takagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.61,Main,Heishi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuujirou, {\i1}CROW{\i0} has the opening pages for issue 49.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.50,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.57,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is perfect, Fukuda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.00,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You're at Niizuma-kun's place now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.07,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Could you put him on for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.30,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "This is perfect"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:41.29,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah sorry, that was a little rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.16,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,Could you just fax me your name, Fukuda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.50,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You only wanna do it in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:50.05,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,You really are as much of a smart-ass as ever, Fukuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.80,Main,Yuujirou,0000,0000,0000,,But I am gonna be around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.68,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.94,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.05,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,This is really good. Could you make it into a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.09,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Your biggest weapon is your artwork, after all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So try to come up with drawings that really fit this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.90,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.07,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're alone today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:12.05,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me your team broke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.86,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.37,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mashiro-kun, right? The one who does the drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.02,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,I actually happen to be looking for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.55,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,to do the artwork for the second-place prize winner of the Story King for the name category.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.67,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be great for—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.33,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't screw around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.39,Main,Somebody,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.19,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, that was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.97,Main,Aida,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.02,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:40.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.64,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The runner-up Story King.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.90,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you did the artwork for that, you might really get popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.77,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If it's popular, it'll naturally get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:53.73,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.28,Main,Mashiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:10:00.30,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you really want to do it, I don't mind apologizing and going to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I get popular, I'll get serialized...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I get serialized...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:11.08,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do do that, you'd better assume you won't be teaming up with Takagi-kun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.82,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Would you still do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Team up with me and we'll become mangakas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.01,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing the artwork and he's doing the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.63,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Fu-sion-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:26.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going nonstop until we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.67,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.53,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what I should do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.50,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still half-hearted about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:52.21,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you should do the artwork for a name by anyone besides Takagi-kun yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.42,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.76,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's so sudden, but do you think you could come in tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.43,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to talk about the scenario with Mashiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.90,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you could answer me honestly, do you not want to be teamed up with him anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who invited him to become mangakas together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:18.90,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But it's my fault things got like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.15,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, I'm still working hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:27.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,and it's something I think might be good enough to get Mashiro to say himself that he wants to team up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.44,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get it done before Mashiro-kun gets serialized by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:35.57,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I see. Then do you think you could leave that part to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:42.76,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,If you listen to what I say, I'm sure you'll get back together and I bet you'll have a hit manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.52,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that you and Mashiro-kun are precisely in tune with each other even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.08,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Enough so that even if you wanted to separate from each other, you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.11,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:03.24,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Mashiro-kun is trying to write a detective story of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:07.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san, did you tell Mashiro-kun what I said I was trying to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.91,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:14.89,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Two people who'd said they'd split up had separately started working on the same kind of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.83,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:20.01,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could hide the fact that you're doing a mystery story up until right before you graduate high school? {KmE: I think this should be shortened. Can't split it cuz there isn't a proper place for it}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:24.35,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, do you think you could write a name for the story that Mashiro-kun is trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.60,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun is always in a rush to get serialized, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:34.23,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,But a detective story is something you should really take your time with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.38,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,So let's take two years and we'll polish up a really good name together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't that mean deceiving Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:47.51,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The way Jack works right now is if something is popular as a one-shot, then it's "Yes, serialize it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:51.45,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Or if it's sent to a serialization meeting and just three chapters are interesting, then it's also "Yes, serialize it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:54.91,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this is limited to works that can survive to the point of being a new series.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.17,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,It's especially hard for newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:02.17,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought for a while now that it's better to take your time on something you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:05.59,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,And if you choose to do that strategy, you'd be the only ones doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:10.74,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,They say that with a battle story you can't wait more than half a year, but with a detective story it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.40,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Take two years and diligently make up a name,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.88,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,have Mashiro-kun draw that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.16,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure you can make something amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.31,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any real point to getting serialized while you're still in high school, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.71,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,So you may as well take your time here to build up your strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:32.10,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold Mashiro-kun back from joining up with someone else or getting serialized alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.13,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:43.07,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,If Mashiro-kun can get serialized on his own, he should be serialized then shouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I talked about this with Mashiro-kun yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,but he looked like he was thinking deep down that he really wanted to be teamed up with you, Takagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:58.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And as proof of that, he turned down doing the art for the runner-up Story King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then would hiding from Mashiro-kun that I'm writing a mystery manga really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:08.98,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Mashiro-kun would want to rush it toward serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.04,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that for his sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, for both your sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.75,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You should prepare a well-honed name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.20,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, the detective story that Mashiro-kun was working on was—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:23.92,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:29.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,If I heard that, I would end up writing a name matching the protagonist that Mashiro-kun thought of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:32.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, with my own skill, I'll win the Story King or whatever it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:37.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,and if at that time Mashiro still says that he's okay with joining up with me, then I will! {qc}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.49,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.17,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,You're right....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.52,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,What you said was more logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.37,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,What I said might have been a case of an adult getting his thoughts twisted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.86,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'll be awaiting an interesting original story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.20,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's plenty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:58.57,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now even if Takagi-kun hears from Mashiro-kun about him writing a detective story, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:01.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he definitely won't tell him that he's drawing one as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:05.09,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He'll draw an interesting name no matter what it takes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.90,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't get over how you two split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Miyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:29.70,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll get you two to make up, I'll do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We're not really in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.11,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, just name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:35.26,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll seriously do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, there's really nothing you need to fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.62,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Man, names really are hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.59,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin's amazing, how does he always do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,How do I write names?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.87,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,First, compose the general idea in your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:02.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,then write out the script, and then divide it into panels so it fits the number of pages?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.79,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:08.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,, I watched him work on it on his computer all summer vacation, so I'm totally sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:11.99,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin did all that hard work and he still couldn't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.00,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,If you think you can't, then why not do it together—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm still gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.44,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to do this for Azuki's sake too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.89,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's why I said do it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:37.18,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,You were on to something when you went home, but I haven't heard any rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.29,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:42.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. Little by little, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:43.96,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.25,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing a one-shot for the main magazine this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.98,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I sent in a name for serialization, but it was a no go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.06,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,They said to run it as a one-shot first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.31,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,That editorial department never knows real talent when they see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.24,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But that's really amazing, to be running in the main magazine and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.14,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.91,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't all that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.38,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't get popular, my serialization name's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.88,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Nakai-san's really gotten into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:10.42,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get what they're about, but the drawing's he's doing aren't like name drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.84,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,They're like friggin' paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.36,Up of Main,Eiji,0000,0000,0000,,Flying apple skin! {Seriously, that's what the manga has, and you can hear it in the background.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:16.21,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,It was only for a little while, but you worked with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:19.60,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,You're now part of the Niizuma Group, no, the Fukuda Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.64,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,So let's try our hardest to change Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.63,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda Group?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.35,Main,Fukuda,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, and keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.96,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.28,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuda-san and Nakai-san are both pumping out names...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:40.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It was on late at night again, but Azuki became a regular on a second anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:42.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,really become a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.34,Main,Azuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They dissolved the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:56.50,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Takagi told me not to say anything, but... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,100 yen a page, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:12.98,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trusting you to do good copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You finished a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I did five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:21.07,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Five whole names? That's incredible, I haven't even finished one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Detective? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.61,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,A name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.81,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant, why is it a detective story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:32.21,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear from Hattori-san I was doing a detective story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:32.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard it a month after I started on my detective story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working on it ever since I saw the cell phone novel site at Miyoshi's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and how they take mystery stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:45.76,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it was on the day you called me at her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:48.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's the day I quit as Eiji's assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it's the same day I got the idea for doing a detective story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:57.40,Main,Hattori,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that you and Mashiro-kun are precisely in tune with each other even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We sure are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:05.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We shifted in the same direction on our own on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.19,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We look like idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:17.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That Hattori-san sure is a schemer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:26.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there was no way I could deceive you for two whole years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd have to do it with Azuki and Miyoshi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:31.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we tell Hattori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.62,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we just tell him the truth and go on like normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.77,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, this kinda feels too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:43.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You got mad at me for not finishing a name by the end of summer vacation and it ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:47.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest with you, I wasn't really that angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.07,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:53.44,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought the reason why you couldn't finish the name was because you were playing around with Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But I know now that that was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.96,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I might've just been jealous of Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:03.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,After what's happened today, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I need you, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about we fool Hattori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Fool him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:22.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san is having us write separately right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.94,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,In half a year, we both tell him "I haven't finished a name yet."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.23,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And in that time we can do as much as we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of doing the three names you need for serialization, we'll do ten chapters. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:37.03,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hattori-san said to hide it for two years, but there's no way I could wait that long anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:37.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:42.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It is true that it's better to take our time with a detective story, but two years is too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.09,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.78,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We don't rush and we carefully work out the name in half a year together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.85,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh good, that sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We'll deceive Hattori-san! That's the specialty of the detective I came up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.02,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We're even in tune on this sorta thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty different from Hattori-san's plan, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.21,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,He said so himself, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Mangakas have to go higher than their editors!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:05.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.89,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess our team was only dissolved for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think it was a little too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:12.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.11,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for us to work separately, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:17.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, if we've got that settled, let's head to the work place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.71,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see that deceptive detective you came up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.55,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.45,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.95,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna talk with you two again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:30.45,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ashirogi Muto is two people in one, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We settled that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:35.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,The team is back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we had you worried, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.41,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:43.32,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was so totally worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We're headed to the work place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you nice as an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:47.62,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.21,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:51.84,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:56.04,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I told Miho about your team breaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:58.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I told you not to tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.08,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:03.23,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Miho was really worried this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:07.46,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,But I told her not to butt in and say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:08.05,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:12.21,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending her an email saying our team's back on and I'm sorry for worrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:14.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Send!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:29.41,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, that was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:38.03,Main,Kaya,0000,0000,0000,,So, so, what'd she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:40.74,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you can look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:44.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What? You and Miho talk about stuff like wavelengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:45.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:16.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we're doing a detective story!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:18.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think of my {\i1}Toumei Tantei Skeleton{\i0} ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:20.56,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,A detective story is a great mainstream idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:22.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But what about my Skeleton? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:25.10,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Cooperation and Conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.10,0:24:27.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I think dreams come in many forms.
